		{"id":"91615c611d73ed73","type":"text","text":"### Creation of Humans\nHumans are born from the Red Crystal Tears, as a cry of [[Conflict]] to solve the current blaze.\nAs a race they have short lifes like a flicker of the flame of other races however they are also the ones most ingenious in solution of problems. ","x":-1080,"y":2623,"width":459,"height":217,"color":"1"},
