		{"id":"67db8e5a09bb0ee2","type":"text","text":"##### \"Keeper of Broken\"\nMany recovering addicts make themselves a tattoo of three fae wings. Signifying Grael Stability and Beauties unconditional acceptance. ","x":1995,"y":635,"width":250,"height":189,"color":"6"},
